Assignment 4: Projections and Navigation

How to compile & run:
- in the directory run "make" then run "hw4"

How to change the view when in orthoginal or perspective view:
- to move the view up: up arrow key
- to move the view down: down arrow key
- to move the view left: left arrow key
- to move the view right: right arrow key
- to aoom in and out: PgDn and PgUp
- to reset the view and dim: 0 key

How to walk in first person view:
- to move forward: up arrow key
- to move backward: down arrow key
- to turn left: left arrow key
- to turn right: right arrow key

How to change projection:
- to change the mode: m key
	- first mode is orthoginal
	- second mode is perspective
	- third mode is first person

How to change what you see:
- to show/unshow axis: a key
- to toggle autorotate: r key

How to exit:
- to exit: esc key

Time to do assignment:
- 5 hours